    <li><a href="http://www.bco.org.uk/Research/Publications/The_Market_Cycles.aspx">The Market Cycles</a> - British Council of Offices</li>
    <li><a href="http://www1.uwe.ac.uk/et/research/cts/researchprojectsbytheme/influencingbehaviours/commutingandwellbeing.aspx">Commuting and Wellbeing -</a> University of the West of England</li>
