<p>The <strong>Segregated Cycle Infrastructure</strong> evidence pack, which we developed, compiles monitoring and evidence about the impacts and benefits of our cycling programme, with a focus on new segregated infrastructure.</p>
<p>It shows that impact of the segregated cycle infrastructure that we've delivered has been largely positive. It shows significant increases in the number of people now cycling on these routes, and 5% more people move across Blackfriars Bridge by all modes of transport than before the segregated lanes were installed.</p>
